# Here adjust environment variables based on your need, available options are:
# - `ADMIN_USER_NPUB` (required): Admin user's Nostr public key (npub format) Get your npub from your Nostr client or generate one
# - `OIDC_ISSUER` (required): issuer URL used by discovery and tokens (example: `http://localhost:8082`)
# - `OIDC_ALLOW_INSECURE` (optional, defaults to `false`): set to `true` only for local HTTP development
